<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lv">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Edijs — Portfolio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>Edijs — HTML5, 2D animācijas un dizains</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="#html5">HTML5 Baneri</a>
